README

Setup networking to DEBUG using Visual studio
1) docker network create -d bridge --gateway=172.19.0.1 --subnet=172.19.0.0/24 tiny_url_network
2) change docker-compose.yml
    a) define external network 
        networks: 
            default:
                external:
                name: tiny_url_network
    b) set static ip to mongodb and change command to bind_ip_all
            networks:
                default:
                    ipv4_address: 172.19.0.2
            command: mongod --bind_ip_all
3) docker-compose up
4) edit csproj to include <DockerfileRunArguments>--network=tiny_url_network</DockerfileRunArguments> inside property group